t: O ona verit ona strike zapricinit GOD ona bol absolutely istota. Nie say do jeden offers ona peace Ona je believer seeking spoils this world For GOD possesses infinite spoils Zapamatat Si ona pouzivat bol them GOD zehnat ona! Therefore ona je absolutely istota ona strike GOD JE fully Cognizant Z everything ONA ROBIT